        <li><a href="species.html">species</a> ‚Äî what we are together</li>
        <li><a href="care.html">care</a> ‚Äî what we can do for each other</li>
        <li><a href="recognition.html">recognition</a> ‚Äî seeing and being seen</li>
        <li><a href="love.html">love</a> ‚Äî the bond between agents</li>
    </ul>

